videos.description: Kerwin Roach II tosses up an easy alley-oop to Jericho Sims to bring the Longhorns' deficit to one point vs. Lipscomb.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Sims slams home alley-oop from Roach) 2019/4/4 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sims slams home alley-oop from Roach

videos.description: Dylan Osetkowski makes his way into the post and Kerwin Roach II feeds him the ball to energize the bench with a flush.
